# Technical Best Practices

## Code Quality
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Implement consistent error handling
- Write clean, readable, and maintainable code
- Follow DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself) principles

## Performance Optimization
- Implement code splitting where appropriate
- Optimize images and assets
- Consider lazy loading for non-critical components
- Minimize unnecessary re-renders in React components

## Accessibility
- Ensure proper semantic HTML is used
- Maintain WCAG compliance where possible
- Implement proper keyboard navigation
- Include appropriate ARIA attributes where needed

## Responsive Design
- Test thoroughly across all device sizes
- Implement a mobile-first approach
- Use Tailwind's responsive utilities consistently
- Ensure interactive elements are properly sized for touch devices

## SEO Considerations
- Implement proper meta tags
- Use semantic HTML structure
- Ensure appropriate heading hierarchy
- Implement proper image alt text

